# lowcode-bpmn

Go BPMN 2.0 engine microservice. JSON process definitions; no XML, no legacy stage orchestrator.

## Packages

- `internal/engine` — execution; `engine.Store` is the persistence boundary
- `internal/bpmn` — model, validation, conditions (incl. dot paths like `item.kk >= 10`)
- `internal/api` — Chi HTTP; errors `{ error, code }`
- `internal/store/open.go` — `STORE_BACKEND`: `db` | `file` | `memory`

## Invariants

- `userTask`: multi-sign modes `any|all|sequential` (或签/会签/顺签); complete requires `assignee` when multiple assignees
- Deploy bumps version; instances pin snapshot at start
- New store methods → implement in `memory`, `gormstore`, `filestore`

## Commands

```bash
go test ./...
go run ./cmd/server
```

See `AGENTS.md` and `ARCHITECTURE.md` for API and layout details.
